            <title>[OAK-8490] FilterProviderImpl.getFilter may fail if principal cache enabled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-8490</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
